matches.awarded_notes: Awarded: The match could not be played due to eight players from Prishtina testing positive for Coronavirus and the whole second team being put into quarantine by the Gibraltarian authorities. Lincoln Red Imps were subsequently awarded a technical 3–0 victory by UEFA.

advancements.advanced_notes: Group winners advanced directly to Round of 16
advancements.wild_card_notes: Group runners-up advanced to Knockout Round play-offs
advancements.transferred_notes: Third-placed teams transferred to Europa Conference League
